{"tid":324021,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日覺得自己好迷糊","createTime":"2017-07-16T06:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T06:41:03.000Z","uid":44050,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d0349765d0c54ea7b085fc35cf134288f302e69","tid":324021,"uid":44050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"思維上唔清醒，睇既野唔真實，總係覺得有層霧咁，日日都覺得自己未訓醒<br />\n<br />\n另一樣野係成日好空虛，每日返工放工，放假打機睇劇，毫無寄托<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea998d6cb484bd3e2275752234fadef2d1d0028","tid":324021,"uid":3924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4471891346e836113f54adab82df65c2a6b93f","tid":324021,"uid":44050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"日日都好似成左藥咁  混混沌沌<br />\n<br />\n放假特別嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caf28c6ca48aae04a747b21d3bebdbbaebb7193","tid":324021,"uid":44050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d119629502318a66fbc5de1786b39d944bdc09","tid":324021,"uid":98878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得生活過得太個安穩 個人會愈黎愈唔知自己想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望bro可以搵到自己有興趣嘅事物嚟沖激一下生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42963ac1ecb2951e94cb4db292e4317327c64e97","tid":324021,"uid":104454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"試過有幾個月日日都keep住依種狀態<br />\n<br />\n個感覺真係好難解釋，好似龍珠入左重力室咁<br />\n<br />\n好似有把鎖鎖住自己個腦部份既運作能力咁<br />\n<br />\n過左個排好番啲，雖然平時都唔係話好醒，但果種感覺係蠢上加蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家都唔知點解會咁"},{"pi